patthana23.33:1.1: Namicchattaniyataṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā sammattaniyato kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā cha …pe… avigate cha.
patthana23.33:2.1: Namicchattaniyataṁ naakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā micchattaniyato akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā cha …pe… avigate cha.
patthana23.33:3.1: Namicchattaniyataṁ naabyākataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca aniyato abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā cha, adhipatiyā cha …pe… avigate cha.
